hysical-music-sales-set-for-first-increase-in-20-years-3775262"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>实体音乐日益流行的消息传出后，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354">英国独立唱片店数量创 10 年来新高</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-vinyl-sales-2023-reach-highest-level-since-1990-3563676">英国黑胶唱片销量也创 1990 年以来最高水平</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-record-store-opens-in-limerick-3782616">《新唱片店在利默里克开业》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
